> Did anyone succeed in installing 6x9 inch speakers in the
> lower part of the front door without cutting the door ?

Troy's bus has some mounted in the doors. They're installed diagonally to
fit the opening.

I liked Hippo's solution (over on the Samba): He made new panels to go from
the top of the kick panels to the edge of the dash and mounted speakers
there.


